{"tid":1602984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要上前排首先要學識向後褪","createTime":"2019-09-29T14:43:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T15:29:49.000Z","uid":77393,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2306c8129c7d243efc7b44fdbc82f6cecdd54225","tid":1602984,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:43:35.000Z","msg":"街頭戰已經三個月有多 企中前排嘅人仍然慣性後退嘅時候轉身行 今日同fd已經不斷提 但根本冇人聽<br />\n<br />\n大家記得係要面向前方 向後褪<br />\n同時必須保持隊形<br />\n<br />\n背對敵人永遠係大忌<br />\n第一 唔會準確知對方嘅行動<br />\n第二 後排嘅人只會恐慌<br />\n第三 一去冇回頭 隊形就會散<br />\n第四 對家沖散隊形就會有手足落單<br />\n<br />\n如果手足唔打算打嘅 不妨一早留定啲空間等前線手足可以撤後 唔好留戀企前排觀戰<br />\n<br />\n後排嘅係可以轉身慢慢行 睇情況而定 但講緊中前排嘅要學識向後褪！<br />\n同時一早唔打算郁手嘅麻煩留定多啲空間畀前線手足！<br />\n仲有企中前排嘅 玩電話都唔該警覺周圍情況 有事起上嚟唔單止自己出事 會累埋同行手足<br />\n<br />\n求大家儘快覺醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f8c12b0d12470c5424d869a0719f7238013ce6","tid":1602984,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:44:25.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"07fcb5515f17ca671277d60dd33206d25d767fcc","tid":1602984,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:44:35.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"58aa07bc7f9bf7fa5f3716304a80f351c93733bf","tid":1602984,"uid":312412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:44:37.000Z","msg":"[twitter懶人包]全部同我入泥！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1602587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1602587</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"606f66cfa9560550525a408c3b18f327f07c0396","tid":1602984,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:44:46.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"17e943ba9aa7f054f0c32b452094fe7f5eb84022","tid":1602984,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T14:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3eb2fc73ea7fccb92085558cf050efe87d5cc55","tid":1602984,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike